---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Thank You">
    <div class="min-h-[60vh] flex items-center justify-center px-4">
        <div class="text-center max-w-lg mx-auto">
            <div class="mb-8 flex justify-center">
                <div
                    class="w-24 h-24 bg-mint/20 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center animate-pulse-slow"
                >
                    <svg
                        xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                        class="h-12 w-12 text-mint"
                        fill="none"
                        viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                        stroke="currentColor"
                    >
                        <path
                            stroke-linecap="round"
                            stroke-linejoin="round"
                            stroke-width="2"
                            d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"
                        ></path>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>

            <h1
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-rounded font-bold text-text-dark mb-6"
            >
                お問い合わせ<br class="md:hidden" />ありがとうございます
            </h1>

            <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed mb-12">
                メッセージ送信が完了しました。<br />
                内容を確認次第、担当者よりご連絡させていただきます。<br />
                今しばらくお待ちください。
            </p>

            <a
                href="/"
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 rounded-full border border-gray-300 text-gray-500 font-bold tracking-widest hover:border-sakura-vivid hover:text-sakura-vivid transition-all duration-300 group"
            >
                <span
                    class="transform group-hover:-translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                    >&larr;</span
                >
                TOPページへ戻る
            </a>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>
